{"title":"我们的演唱组","authors":["钱红春"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的演唱组"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军某部战士　钱红春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的演唱组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装备很朴素，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两把胡琴一支笛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外加竹板和锣鼓；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别瞧家当少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节目精采又丰富。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的演唱组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能歌也能舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行军路上唱一段，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"训练间隙说快书；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到哪里演到哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劲头实在足。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的演唱组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能文更能武，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射击、投弹和刺杀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练出一手硬功夫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台上都是好演员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台下都是小老虎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的演唱组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都把雄心树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为革命，演节目，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化阵地守牢固，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不忘阶级斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的话紧记住！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}